292
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,720
Then let's do something of ours.

293
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,400
Something of ours.

294
00:20:25,599 --> 00:20:26,480
What is it?

295
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,119
