297
00:20:33,839 --> 00:20:35,519
I've already found a place to take pictures.

298
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,079
Let's go now.

299
00:20:58,359 --> 00:20:59,720
Is my location wrong?

300
00:21:00,599 --> 00:21:01,359
No.

301
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,279
It's so hard to walk here.

302
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:08,119
No wonder the taxi left us.

303
00:21:10,119 --> 00:21:10,960
This place of his

304
00:21:21,599 --> 00:21:22,480
Zhai Qiuyu

305
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,119
