374
00:24:29,799 --> 00:24:30,599
Get out!

375
00:24:34,279 --> 00:24:35,880
Li Youen treats him like a treasure.

376
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:36,960
He said he'd smash them.

377
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,799
Li Youen won't hold back.

378
00:24:41,839 --> 00:24:42,839
Zhai Qiuyu

379
00:24:43,119 --> 00:24:44,799
