496
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,079
I can do anything

497
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,440
I'll do it for you now

498
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:27,640
I'll do it for you.

499
00:30:28,119 --> 00:30:28,799
